usly guessed. The authors urge us to protect the biological wealth of our Earth and keep it from being destroyed by human activity.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 7aNATURE / Environmental Conservation & Protection.2bisacsh1 aEhrlich, Paul R., eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aTurnbull, Christine.40uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/9780300127188?locatt=mode:legacy40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300127188423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300127188/original  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles